Fixes: 1da177e4c3f4 ("Linux-2.6.12-rc2")
Reported-by: syzbot+f3a497f02c389d86ef16@syzkaller.appspotmail.com
Closes: https://lore.kernel.org/netdev/6920855a.a70a0220.2ea503.0058.GAE@google.com/T/#u
